  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion:

        All adult (≥ 18 years) patients admitted for the first time to the participating ICUs will
        be included.

        Exclusion:

        Not critically Ill, admitted for low risk monitoring, planned ICU admissions for routine
        postoperative surveillance for less than 24 hours after uncomplicated surgery, readmission
        and transferred from outside ICU.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
